{"tid":728215,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：若果沒有我出現　美國可能正與北韓開戰","createTime":"2018-07-03T15:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T15:50:49.000Z","uid":150685,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"434b9f1a733e0ec5fe530ecc0211af47f0999a9e","tid":728215,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1404993_1_L_20180703193810.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1404993_1_L_20180703193810.jpg&h=abee551c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普在社交網站表示，與北韓有很多良好的對話，過程順利。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又表示，過去八個月以來，北韓都未有試射火箭或進行核試，令整個亞洲都感到興奮，只有反對黨派及製造假新聞的媒體在投訴，特朗普又表示，若果沒有他的出現，現時可能正與北韓開戰。<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮證實，國務卿蓬佩奧將會再次訪問北韓，討論棄核問題。發言人桑德斯表示，蓬佩奧將在本月5日，即星期四啟程前往平壤，與北韓領袖金正恩以及他的團隊會面。在峰會舉行之前，蓬佩奧曾經以中央情報局局長、以及國務卿的身份，兩度訪問北韓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1404993-20180703.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1404993-20180703.htm&d=EvzYZr7kiv8ZnmPiOjxQ97r9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=fcb3af09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1404993-20180703.htm&h=18fae288\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1404993-20180703.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8fccd4bfe5c34a9448dfb35f17a5538d322ad005","tid":728215,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:33:51.000Z","msg":"侵仔幾時拎和平獎"},{"pid":"a313d99cff915d8ca28a755704566b51f402c141","tid":728215,"uid":47268,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:38:40.000Z","msg":"前任黑鬼唔知做過啲咩"},{"pid":"848a322995731f5df67e9c6f215c33caa39d337c","tid":728215,"uid":8949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:50:49.000Z","msg":"我就唔信班左膠會開戰"}]}